    "sn1.76:5.4": "Compare the “roadblocks for wealth” at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/an10.73/en/sujato#2.2'>AN 10.73:2.2</a>. This shows that <i lang='pi' translate='no'>vitta</i> (“wealth”) is correct here, not <i lang='pi' translate='no'>citta</i> (“mind”). "
